\section{Measuring the Strength of Evidence}

\subsection*{Example 1.2: Rock Paper Scissors}

\begin{enumerate}
  \item
    $H_0$: $\pi = 1/3$
    
    $H_a$: $\pi < 1/3$
    
    Test statistic:  $\hat p = 0.167$ (the sample proportion of 1/6)
	\item
		We simulate a world in which $\pi = 1/3$:
<<Figure1.7, cache=TRUE>>=
